trafpy.benchmarker.tools module¶

trafpy.benchmarker.tools.gen_benchmark_demands(path_to_save=None, save_format='json', separate_files=False, load_prev_dists=True, overwrite=False)[source]¶

If separate_files, will save each load, repeat and, and benchmark to separate files in a common folder. This can help with memory since not storing everything in one large file.

If slot size is not None, will also generate an sqlite database for the slots_dict dictionary. This is useful if later during simulations want to have pre-computed slots_dict rather than computing & storing them in memory.
